Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.99,0:01:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahata-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:01:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eu fiz um delicioso chá.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Você pode experimentar um pouco?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.95,0:02:07.86,xicara,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(255,310)}Amor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:08.74,xicara,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(110,480,90,430[120,130])}Amor
